  "content": "Powerhouse's Document Synchronization Protocol (DocSync) does not rely on a centralized server but can run peer-to-peer. It is also storage agnostic, so there is no lock-in. Users have the option to rely on decentralized, centralized, or local storage solutions. This reflects blockchain's decentralization principle adapted for practical organizational needs.",
